-BLONDE BOY:
DID YOU SEE ANY YET?

02:16.832 --> 02:18.138
-TWO BABES JUST
TOOK THEIR TOPS OFF.

02:18.268 --> 02:19.791
-OH, LET ME SEE.
-HOLD ON, HOLD ON, MAN.

02:19.922 --> 02:21.097
-BLONDE BOY: COME ON,
LET ME SEE, DON'T HOG IT.

02:21.228 --> 02:21.880
-BRUNETTE BOY:
WAIT, HOLD ON, HOLD ON.

02:22.011 --> 02:23.055
-COME ON.

02:26.929 --> 02:28.017
-WHOA. WHOA, WHOA, WHOA!

02:38.506 --> 02:39.724
-BOY, IF WE DON'T
SHUT THIS DOWN,

02:39.855 --> 02:41.161
SOMEONE'S GONNA GET KILLED.

02:42.640 --> 02:45.121
THIS IS THE LOS ANGELES
COUNTY LIFEGUARDS.

02:45.252 --> 02:48.516
NUDE SUNBATHING ON
L.A. COUNTY BEACHES IS ILLEGAL.

02:48.646 --> 02:50.822
COVER UP IMMEDIATELY
OR YOU WILL BE CITED.

02:52.346 --> 02:55.218
-DON'T BE INTIMIDATED,
LET 'EM CITE US

02:55.349 --> 02:58.439
FOR EXERCISING OUR GOD-GIVEN
RIGHTS AS HUMAN BEINGS.

02:58.961 --> 03:01.572
-NUDITY IS A
GOD-GIVEN BIRTHRIGHT.

03:02.182 --> 03:05.359
THESE COWARDS DON'T EVEN DESERVE
TO BE NAKED ON THE BEACH.

03:05.968 --> 03:07.099
-WE'RE WITH YOU, HOWARD.

03:08.100 --> 03:09.841
-THEY WON'T HAVE
THE NERVE TO CITE US.

03:09.972 --> 03:11.539
-RIGHT ON, NUDITY!

03:11.669 --> 03:13.628
NUDITY IS FREEDOM!

03:13.758 --> 03:15.282
NUDITY IS FREEDOM!

03:15.891 --> 03:17.936
-USE EXTREME CAUTION
HIKING UP THE CLIFF.

03:18.067 --> 03:19.851
KEEP ON THE PATH.

03:19.982 --> 03:21.113
-COWARDS!

03:21.244 --> 03:22.245
WEASELS!

03:23.855 --> 03:27.424
-LOOKS LIKE WE'VE GOT A FEW
STUBBORN DIE HARDS OUT THERE.

03:27.555 --> 03:30.601
A COUPLE OF VERY ATHLETIC
LOOKING YOUNG LADIES

03:30.732 --> 03:32.037
AND WHAT LOOKS LIKE...

03:34.301 --> 03:35.563
A PILLAR OF STRENGTH
IN HIS COMMUNITY.

03:35.693 --> 03:37.042
-I THINK THERE
SHOULD BE SOME BEACHES

03:37.173 --> 03:38.740
WHERE NUDE SUNBATHING
IS MANDATORY.

03:39.523 --> 03:41.046
-MANDATORY?

03:41.177 --> 03:42.134
-YEAH, THERE'S NOTHING
BETTER THAN LYING ON A HOT,

03:42.265 --> 03:44.267
SANDY BEACH NAKED.

03:44.398 --> 03:45.790
-AND WHAT WOULD
THE LIFEGUARD WEAR?

03:45.921 --> 03:47.314
-SUNBLOCK.

03:47.444 --> 03:48.837
-WHERE WOULD YOU
PUT THE PATCH?

03:49.446 --> 03:50.839
-USE YOUR IMAGINATION, NEWMIE.

03:51.622 --> 03:53.145
-OH, OH, OH, OH.

03:53.276 --> 03:54.451
ALL RIGHT, YOU TWO, TWO
OF US ARE GONNA HAVE TO GO

03:54.582 --> 03:55.713
IN ON THE SEA-DOOS.

03:55.844 --> 03:57.498
-NAKED OR DRESSED?
-DRESSED.

03:57.628 --> 04:00.283
-I VOLUNTEER.
-YEAH, RIGHT, NEWMIE.

04:08.160 --> 04:09.901
-CODY: I'LL DEAL WITH HIM,
YOU HANDLE THE WOMEN.

04:10.032 --> 04:10.902
-OKAY?

04:18.170 --> 04:19.214
-HOW YOU DOING?

04:21.608 --> 04:24.351
HOPE YOU USE SUNBLOCK
IN THE EXPOSED AREAS.

04:24.481 --> 04:26.222
-HEY, APPRECIATE THE CONCERN.

04:27.049 --> 04:28.442
-THEN I HOPE YOU CAN
APPRECIATE THE FACT

04:28.572 --> 04:30.574
THAT NUDE SUNBATHING
IS AGAINST THE LAW.

04:30.705 --> 04:34.274
-THE LAWS OF MAN,
NOT THE LAWS OF NATURE.

04:35.013 --> 04:35.971
[GIGGLING]

04:36.754 --> 04:38.626
-LOOK, MAN,
I'M A NATURE LOVER TOO.

04:38.756 --> 04:40.454
IF YOU WANNA SUN YOUR BUNS,
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE

04:40.584 --> 04:42.543
TO DO IT IN THE PRIVACY
OF YOUR OWN BACKYARD.

04:43.108 --> 04:46.547
-SUN YOUR BUNS. WE PREFER
THE BEACH, NATURE BOY.

04:52.379 --> 04:53.945
[GIGGLING]

04:55.207 --> 04:56.208
-YOUR TURN.

04:58.863 --> 05:00.735
[SOOTHING MUSIC]

05:09.918 --> 05:11.180
-C.J.: LADIES, I'M
AFRAID YOU'RE GONNA HAVE

05:11.311 --> 05:12.399
TO PUT SOMETHING ON.

05:12.529 --> 05:14.488
-I SUNBATHE NUDE
ALL OVER EUROPE.

05:16.707 --> 05:18.492
-I KNOW, BUT THIS
IS CALIFORNIA.

05:18.622 --> 05:20.363
YOU WOULDN'T THINK
IT WOULD BE SUCH A BIG DEAL.

05:20.494 --> 05:22.278
-CAN'T YOU JUST LEAVE
US ALONE AND RESCUE

05:22.409 --> 05:23.540
SOMEONE WHO NEEDS YOUR HELP?

05:24.236 --> 05:25.716
-WELL, WE TRY AND PREVENT
PROBLEMS BEFORE THEY HAPPEN,

05:25.847 --> 05:27.849
AND WHAT YOU GUYS ARE DOING
IS A LITTLE DANGEROUS.

05:27.979 --> 05:29.546
-WE'RE WEARING SUNBLOCK.

05:30.547 --> 05:33.028
-NOT DANGEROUS
FOR YOU, DANGEROUS
FOR THOSE GUYS UP THERE.

05:33.637 --> 05:35.030
THEY KEEP TRYING
TO SNEAK A PEEK.

05:39.339 --> 05:42.951
-YOUNG MAN, YOU ARE THREATENING
OUR FREEDOM OF RELIGION.

05:43.908 --> 05:45.432
-GETTING NAKED
IS YOUR RELIGION?

05:45.562 --> 05:47.390
-YES, WE WORSHIP THE SUN.
THIS IS OUR TEMPLE.

05:48.739 --> 05:51.002
-I'M AFRAID TEMPLE
IS CLOSED FOR TODAY.

05:51.699 --> 05:52.917
YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE TO
COVER UP OR I'LL CITE YOU

05:53.048 --> 05:54.136
FOR INDECENT EXPOSURE.

05:54.266 --> 05:55.355
-CITE AWAY, SONNY.

05:58.967 --> 06:00.577
-I CAN HAVE YOU
ARRESTED, YOU KNOW.

06:01.186 --> 06:02.492
-JUST MAKE SURE
TO INVITE THE PRESS.

06:04.451 --> 06:06.061
-ALL RIGHT, MAN,
IT'S YOUR BUTT.

06:07.976 --> 06:09.456
LET'S GO, COME ON.

06:11.936 --> 06:13.198
-C.J.: TIME TO GO.

06:17.377 --> 06:19.161
-I DON'T CARE WHAT
YOU HEARD, MA'AM.

06:19.291 --> 06:22.599
THERE ARE NO NUDE BEACHES
IN MALIBU OR ZUMA.

06:23.470 --> 06:25.559
IF YOU'RE WORRIED
ABOUT TAN LINES,

06:25.689 --> 06:27.387
JUST GO OUT AND BUY
A SELF TANNING PRODUCT.

06:28.257 --> 06:29.127
YOU'RE WELCOME.

06:31.042 --> 06:32.000
-YEAH, THERE IS.

06:33.480 --> 06:35.569
-WHAT?
-THERE'S A NUDE BEACH IN ZUMA.

06:35.699 --> 06:37.092
J.B. AND CONNOR
WENT THERE TODAY.

06:37.222 --> 06:39.747
THEY INVITED ME,
BUT I TOLD THEM I'D RATHER SPEND

06:39.877 --> 06:40.704
THE DAY WITH YOU.

06:40.835 --> 06:42.489
-ARE YOU FEELING OKAY?

06:42.619 --> 06:44.142
YOU'D ACTUALLY RATHER SPEND
THE DAY WITH YOUR FATHER

06:44.273 --> 06:45.970
THEN WITH YOUR FRIENDS
SPYING ON A NUDE BEACH?

06:46.101 --> 06:48.059
-I KNOW, I KNOW IT
SOUNDS CRAZY TO ME, TOO,

06:48.190 --> 06:50.627
BUT I HAVEN'T BEEN ABLE
TO DO MUCH WITH YOU LATELY

06:51.802 --> 06:52.890
AND I GUESS I MISS
HANGING OUT WITH YOU.

06:53.587 --> 06:54.979
-YEAH, I KNOW, PAL.

06:55.110 --> 06:56.764
I MISS YOU WHEN YOU'RE
AT YOUR MOM'S TOO.

06:56.894 --> 06:58.592
AS SOON AS YOU GET BACK,
I'M EITHER WORKING

06:58.722 --> 06:59.897
OR YOU'RE OUT
WITH YOUR FRIENDS.

07:00.507 --> 07:02.334
-WELL, WHY DON'T I HANG
OUT HERE WHILE YOU WORK

07:02.465 --> 07:03.901
AND WE CAN GO DO
SOMETHING LATER.

07:04.032 --> 07:05.468
-WHAT DO YOU SAY
I TAKE THE AFTERNOON OFF?

07:05.599 --> 07:06.382
WE GET A BOAT AND
WE GO WAKE BOARDING?

07:06.513 --> 07:07.731
-RIGHT, SOUNDS GREAT.

07:07.862 --> 07:09.080
-WE NEED A THIRD
PERSON AS A SPOTTER.

07:09.820 --> 07:10.647
-I CAN CALL JENNY.

07:11.300 --> 07:13.215
-CALL HER.
-HOBIE: RIGHT.

07:17.567 --> 07:20.831
-OKAY, WE'RE OFF THE SHELF,
NOTHING BUT CLEAR BLUE SEA

07:20.962 --> 07:21.963
UNDERNEATH US NOW.

07:22.485 --> 07:24.095
-'KAY, THE VALVES
ARE COMPUTERIZED,

07:24.226 --> 07:25.923
SO THEY'RE AUTOMATICALLY
GONNA ADJUST THE AIR VOLUME

07:26.054 --> 07:27.882
IN YOUR DRY SUIT
AS YOU GO DEEPER.

07:28.012 --> 07:29.710
AT A HUNDRED FEET, THEY'LL
REPLACE YOUR TRAVEL GAS.

07:29.840 --> 07:33.235
-ENRICHED NITRATE 36, RIGHT?
-EXACTLY.

07:33.365 --> 07:36.978
OXYGEN IS AT 16%, NITROGEN 34%

07:37.108 --> 07:38.762
AND HELIUM AT 50%.

07:38.893 --> 07:40.590
-[LAUGHS] SHE'S GONNA
SOUND LIKE A CHIPMUNK, GUYS.

07:40.721 --> 07:42.505
[LAUGHING]

07:42.636 --> 07:43.941
-YEAH, BUT SHE'LL BE ABLE TO
DIVE DEEPER, STAY DOWN LONGER

07:44.072 --> 07:44.899
AND DECOMPRESS FASTER.

07:45.029 --> 07:46.248
-IF IT WORKS.

07:47.467 --> 07:48.946
-NEELY, IF YOU DON'T
WANT TO DO THIS.

07:49.077 --> 07:50.513
-ARE YOU KIDDING?

07:50.644 --> 07:51.558
I WANTED TO BE A TEST
PILOT WHEN I WAS LITTLE,

07:51.688 --> 07:53.734
BUT I HATED TO FLY.

07:53.864 --> 07:55.562
I LOVE TO DIVE,
SO THIS IS PERFECT.

07:55.692 --> 07:57.651
-SO HOW DEEP CAN
SHE GO ON THE TRY MIX?

07:57.781 --> 08:00.958
-WELL, BOTTOM'S ABOUT 400 FEET,
SAY WE GO THE WHOLE WAY.

08:02.003 --> 08:03.004
-SOUNDS GOOD TO ME.

08:03.134 --> 08:05.267
-WAIT A SECOND,
ON 16% OXYGEN?

08:05.397 --> 08:07.269
-WELL, IT WON'T BE
16% OXYGEN.

08:07.922 --> 08:09.576
THE VALVES WILL AUTOMATICALLY
ADJUST THE TRY MIX

08:09.706 --> 08:11.969
DOWN TO 5% OXYGEN, THAT'S
THE BEAUTY OF THE SYSTEM.

08:12.100 --> 08:13.928
-RIGHT, BUT WHAT
ABOUT THE NITROGEN?

08:14.058 --> 08:16.191
I MEAN, WE DON'T WANT
HER TO GET NARCOSIS.

08:16.321 --> 08:17.888
RAPTURE OF THE DEEP, NEELY.

08:18.019 --> 08:19.324
YOU COULD END UP
SEDUCING A BARRACUDA.

08:19.977 --> 08:23.198
-I DO ENOUGH OF THAT ON DRY
LAND, THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

08:23.328 --> 08:24.547
[LAUGHING]

08:30.553 --> 08:32.816
[SIRENS BLARING]

08:42.304 --> 08:44.131
[GROANING]

08:49.093 --> 08:50.921
-THAT'S FABULOUS.

08:51.052 --> 08:52.793
-YOU KNOW, THIS IS
YOUR LAST CHANCE.

08:52.923 --> 08:55.317
PUT ON YOUR CLOTHES OR
YOU'RE GONNA BE ARRESTED.

08:55.447 --> 08:58.407
-YOUNG MAN, WE'RE WILLING
TO BE JAILED FOR OUR BELIEFS.

08:58.538 --> 08:59.626
AREN'T WE, LADIES?

08:59.756 --> 09:01.192
-YES, FOR SURE.

09:01.715 --> 09:03.281
-SUIT YOURSELVES.

09:03.412 --> 09:07.416
-YOU KNOW, YOU HAVE
A PERFECT BODY FOR YOGA.

09:07.547 --> 09:10.027
