SHOULD TAKE MY CLASS.

09:10.637 --> 09:12.334
-NO, THANKS.

09:12.464 --> 09:14.292
-COME ON, CODY, IT'LL BE
GREAT. IT'S GOOD FOR AGILITY.

09:14.423 --> 09:15.816
-YEAH, SHE'S A GOOD TEACHER.

09:15.946 --> 09:18.296
-THIS IS THE SALUTE TO THE SUN.

09:23.171 --> 09:24.476
-IT'S MORE LIKE THE MOON TO ME.

09:24.607 --> 09:27.262
