10:07.781 --> 10:10.174
-I GOT EVERYONE
COMING OUT WITH TOWELS.

10:10.305 --> 10:11.872
-I DON'T KNOW WHAT THE
BIG DEAL ABOUT NUDITY IS.

10:12.002 --> 10:13.525
I MEAN, EVERYBODY
KNOWS WHAT'S THERE.

10:13.656 --> 10:15.963
-THE PEOPLE I SEE, I DON'T
WANNA KNOW WHAT'S THERE.

10:16.093 --> 10:17.312
[LAUGHING]

10:18.226 --> 10:21.055
-MANNY, I'M SORRY, BUT
YOU'RE JUST A LITTLE TOO YOUNG

10:21.185 --> 10:22.447
