10:22.578 --> 10:24.188
-WHAT? I'M GONNA BE 18
IN THREE WEEKS.

10:24.319 --> 10:26.016
-YEAH, BUT YOU'RE
STILL A JUNIOR LIFEGUARD,

10:26.147 --> 10:27.888
AND BESIDES, DON'T YOU HAVE
INCIDENT REPORTS TO FILE?

10:28.018 --> 10:30.847
-INCIDENT REPORTS?
MAN, YOU KNOW WHAT THIS IS?

10:30.978 --> 10:32.762
THIS IS AGE DISCRIMINATION.

10:32.893 --> 10:34.895
-OH, COME ON.

10:35.025 --> 10:36.897
[LAUGHING]

10:38.376 --> 10:41.597
-THIS IS A DENIAL OF
BASIC HUMAN RIGHTS.

10:41.728 --> 10:44.644
THE RIGHT TO BEAR ARMS AND
THE RIGHT TO BEAR LEGS.

10:44.774 --> 10:47.211
THE RIGHT TO BEAR
ANYTHING WE CHOOSE.

10:47.342 --> 10:48.735
